description: Governance of HIV/AIDS Programme in Ukraine

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacity for inclusive governance and coordination of national HIV responses, and for the protection of human rights of people affected by HIV, including women and other vulnerable groups
subproject.description:
1. Capacities of the selected governmental agencies in designing and implementing the effective strategies and programmes to overcome HIV/AIDS epidemic increased
2. Governance and management of HIV/AIDS response at the local level are strengthened to ensure scaling up services for Universal Access to HIV/AIDS prevention, treatment, care, and support
3. Human rights of people affected by HIV, including men who have sex with men, promoted, and their equal access to prevention, treatment, care and support services ensured
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Governance of HIV/AIDS Program
